ewhois-query

Query the ewhois.com engine.
    
* Whois Lookup
* Reverse IP Lookup
* Reverse Adsense ID Lookup
* Reverse Google Analytics ID Lookup

NOTES: 

Each use retrieves the queried page and stores in the 
current working directory (CWD). ewhois-query works on
that file offline e.g. google.com.html. The extension 
should not be specified when using the -N option i.e.
google.com not google.com.html. 

